{"tid":1393773,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"保持醒覺，勿被利用","createTime":"2019-08-01T07:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T08:07:17.000Z","uid":67115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"72aa10e990a18ae1a9c429190c495fb11f20fc08","tid":1393773,"uid":67115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:54:01.000Z","msg":"&diams;️&diams;️&diams;️保持醒覺，勿被利用&diams;️&diams;️&diams;️<br />\n<br />\n圖中係 CIA 心戰教材，細心諗下，「前線小朋友冇錢食飯」中咗幾多？知驚未？<br />\n<br />\n敵人會利用你嘅善心，做 agenda setting。先騎劫一個動人故事 (e.g. 前線小朋友冇錢食飯)，然後製造思維框架 (e.g. 唔好畀 cash)，引導 &ldquo;聰明仔&rdquo; 自己推出如 &ldquo;用儲值八達通&rdquo; 此類萬劫不復的主意，然後讚揚鼓勵。<br />\n<br />\nThe road to hell is paved with good intentions (世上壞事，多為好心做壞事)，切記！<br />\n<br />\nCIA 心戰教材：<a href=\"https://adamchiaramedia.files.wordpress.com/2018/10/cia_psyops.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fadamchiaramedia.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F10%2Fcia_psyops.pdf&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl58RCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=5ca73164\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://adamchiaramedia.files.wordpress.com/2018/10/cia_psyops.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2gVrPNo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2gVrPNo.png&h=c29c18cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8f6296b5c2f86c1edf926d90d704c95e47b9ef2","tid":1393773,"uid":6051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:55:21.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"94854f4bd5a33680612a164a9d884f65c4497b86","tid":1393773,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72aa10e990a18ae1a9c429190c495fb11f20fc08","tid":1393773,"uid":67115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:54:01.000Z","msg":"&diams;️&diams;️&diams;️保持醒覺，勿被利用&diams;️&diams;️&diams;️<br />\n<br />\n圖中係 CIA 心戰教材，細心諗下，「前線小朋友冇錢食飯」中咗幾多？知驚未？<br />\n<br />\n敵人會利用你嘅善心，做 agenda setting。先騎劫一個動人故事 (e.g. 前線小朋友冇錢食飯)，然後製造思維框架 (e.g. 唔好畀 cash)，引導 &ldquo;聰明仔&rdquo; 自己推出如 &ldquo;用儲值八達通&rdquo; 此類萬劫不復的主